				<td colspan="2"><span>This is the small improvement over scream of pain 61 song.
<br />

<br />
It can interrupt casters every 3 seconds.  Does a knockback, no stun, but usually interrupts the spell.  If you are going to be mezing, dots get in the way at times.  Try going into the arena chain wacking this dd on a caster every 3 seconds as you mele them.  It is not a guaranteed win, but it does make their life miserable.  (below every 18 seconds too...18 what a waste.)
<br />

<br />
390's per pulse with the odd 780 criticals.
<br />

<br />
Moose</span></td>
